《'''藥命效應'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Limitless'''''}}）是一部[[美国|美国]]电视剧，于2015年9月22日在[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]首播。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title='Limitless', 'Rush Hour', 'Criminal Minds' Spinoff, 'Code', 'Life' Among CBS Orders|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/limitless-rush-hour-criminal-minds-spinoff-life-in-pieces-jane-lynch-cbs-series-orders-1201423198/|website=[[deadline.com|deadline.com]]|accessdate=7 August 2015|date=May 8, 2015|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126211217/http://deadline.com/2015/05/limitless-rush-hour-criminal-minds-spinoff-life-in-pieces-jane-lynch-cbs-series-orders-1201423198/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CBS premiere">{{cite web|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=CBS Announces Fall Premiere Dates, Including Supergirl and Limitless|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/448665-cbs-announces-fall-premiere-dates-including-supergirl-and-limitless#/slide/1|website=Comingsoon|accessdate=7 August 2015|date=June 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131134602/http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/448665-cbs-announces-fall-premiere-dates-including-supergirl-and-limitless#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Ausiello|first1=Michael|title=CBS Fall Premiere Dates: ''Supergirl'' Gets Big October Launch|url=http://tvline.com/2015/06/09/cbs-premiere-dates-fall-2015-supergirl/|website=TVLine|accessdate=7 August 2015|date=June 9, 2015|archive-date=2015-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813061613/http://tvline.com/2015/06/09/cbs-premiere-dates-fall-2015-supergirl/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本劇是改編自小說《''{{link-en|The Dark Fields|The Dark Fields}}''》的[[逆天潛能|同名電影]]的續集，故事設定於電影版的四年後。2015年10月23日宣布預訂第一季全季22集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/10/23/limitless-earns-full-season-order-at-cbs/480111/|title='Limitless' earns full-season order at CBS|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=TV by the Numbers|date=October 23, 2015|accessdate=October 23, 2015|archive-date=2015-1